# `.optional()`/`.many()` for arg multiplicity,
# `construct!` MACRO using Rust field-init
# shorthand to assemble the final struct, FromStr-
# trait-based type conversion.  Extends cross-
# language CLI taxonomy to SIXTY-NINE library
# variants: **Rust (6→7)**, Go (4), Python (3),
# Crystal 1 OptionParser (R269), Haskell (R270),
# OCaml 1 Cmdliner (R271), C (R272), Java 1
